          "reviewBody": "We are very fortunate & grateful to Windows & all the teachers for taking care of my baby in her life's first schooling journey. Our sincere gratitude to the teachers for contributing to our child's growth & curiosity for learning... Thank you for being so kind & putting all the hard work, patience, dedication for shaping our child's future. Being a COVID era kid the teachers really helped in transforming her social skills. My child was very comfortable & happy at school. Also, we want to express our appreciation for all the love, care & support you had shown to our child. Thank you so much!!",
