          "reviewBody": "A rare gem! By far the best in Noida, hands down! Sonya, Mrs. Baluja and the team of teachers are nurturing and put so much thought into the kids days, activities and their emotional being. The perfect place to start young kids for a strong foundation. As a parent, there’s plenty I’ve learned from them and continue to do so. Thank you Windows for all you do. More power to you!",
