          "reviewBody": "My kids have gone to Windows Play school....It has been a wonderful experience....All the staffs right from the Principal to the Didi's are very caring and doing a fabulous job. Its a very balanced place, not only about the academic or fun activities...they instill some basic values in the children too.",
