          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Always heard that this is the best playschool in Noida. And thankfully we waited till they reopened after covid. It's a perfect blend of warmth and wisdom which is easily evident by seeing the teachers only. Mrs baluja is an experienced lady and I just love how she understands the need of every child alongwith their parents. All the teachers are very supportive and helpful. They prepare the children very well for the interviews. Also it was very thoughtful of them to conduct an orientation for parents regarding the admission process. Overall, It was a very nice experience. Just trust in the Windows Team for they know what they are making child to be - a happy and thoughtful human being !! 😊",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
