            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Seen a huge difference in my daughter's attitude after she started going to windows. Wish there was not this kind of abrupt end of the session due to Corona. She wishes to meet her teachers and as a parent I would strongly request the online sessions to continue so that children still feel that they are a part of the windows school. To be frank my daughter misses her school, teachers and friends a lot. And we too. 😊",
